Package: nichenetr
Type: Package
Title: Linking Extracellular Protein Signals to Target Genes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Robin", "Browaeys", email = "robin.browaeys@ugent.be",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package allows you the investigate intercellular communication from a computational perspective. Functionalities of this package (e.g. including predicting extracellular upstream regulators) build upon a probabilistic model of ligand-target links that was inferred by data-integration.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/browaeysrobin/nichenetr
